<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>vision</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./public/assets/css/stylesponsors.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./public/assets/css/stylepartials.css" />
    <link href="assets/eceaGreen.png" rel="icon" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,500;1,400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script
      defer
      src="https://unpkg.com/sweetalert/dist/sweetalert.min.js"
    ></script>
    <script defer src="./public/assets/js/particles.js"></script>
    <script defer src="./public/assets/js/app.js"></script>
    <script defer src="./public/assets/js/index.js"></script>
    <script defer src="./public/assets/js/alert.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header><%- include('../partials/navbar'); %></header>
    <div class="container">
      <div id="particles-js"></div>
      <div class="banner"></div>
      <div class="sponsors">
        <div class="title">SPONSORS</div>
        <h3 class="sponsor-category">Title Sponsor</h3>
        <div class="sponsors-grid">
          <div class="grid-item grid1">
            <div class="img-container">
              <img src="../../public/assets/images/title-sponsor.jpeg" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="sponsor-category">Co Sponsor</h3>
        <div class="sponsors-grid">
          <div class="grid-item grid1">
            <div class="img-container">
              <img src="../../public/assets/images/co-sponsor.jpeg" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="sponsor-category">Workshop Sponsors</h3>
        <div class="sponsors-grid">
          <div class="grid-item grid1">
            <div class="img-container">
              <img src="../../public/assets/images/robo-club.png" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-item grid2">
            <div class="img-container">
              <img src="../../public/assets/images/aaceg-logo.png" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="sponsor-benefits">
      <h1>sponsor benefits</h1>
      <div class="content">
        <div class="right">
          <h2>MAIN SPONSOR ₹2,00,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. The name of your company will precede the name of VISION wherever
            they appear and henceforth your company and DECE presents "VISION
            2022". <br />2. The name of the main sponsor will appear on all
            official VISION products including T-Shirt, posters, delegate kits,
            invitations, newspaper advertisement and bags.<br />
            3. A banner will be put up in the auditorium and the department
            entrance(offline).<br />
            4. The main sponsor logo and name will be featured in the VISION
            website.<br />
            5. Benefits include a full-page colour advertisement in the souvenir
            and announcement between the events and workshops.<br />
            6. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>CO – SPONSOR ₹1,00,000</h2>
          <p>
            1.The name of the co - sponsor will appear on all official VISION
            products including T-Shirt, posters, delegate kits, invitations,
            newspaper advertisement and bags(offline)<br />
            2. A banner will be put up in the auditorium and the department
            entrance (offline).<br />
            3. The co-sponsor's logo and name will be featured in the VISION
            website. <br />4. Benefits include a full page color advertisement
            in the souvenir and announcement between the events and
            workshops.<br />
            5. The co-sponsor will be the exclusive sponsor for one of the
            events.<br />
            6. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>DAY SPONSOR ₹ 75,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. Whenever an event of the day is advertised, it will be mentioned
            as &ltday Sponsor&gt and &ltEvent Sponsor&gt jointly present
            &ltEvent Name&gt.<br />
            2. A banner will be put up in the auditorium and the department
            entrance(offline). <br />3. The day sponsor logo and name will be
            featured in the VISION website.<br />
            4. Benefits include a full page color advertisement in the souvenir
            and announcement between the events and workshops.<br />
            5. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>T-SHIRT SPONSOR ₹1,50,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. Name and logo of the t-shirt sponsor will feature on the
            t-shirt.<br />
            2. Benefits include a half page advertisement in the souvenir, logo
            on banners and announcements during events and workshops.<br />
            3. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>FOOD SPONSOR ₹1,50,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. A banner will be set up at venues (offline).<br />
            2. Benefits include a full-page advertisement in the souvenir and
            appropriate mention in website.<br />
            3. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>EVENT/WORKSHOP SPONSOR ₹ 30,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. When the event is advertised, it will be mentioned as &ltCompany
            name&gt presents &ltEvent/ Workshop name&gt. <br />2. The company
            name and logo will feature on posters and banners in the
            department.<br />
            3. Benefits include a half page advertisement in the souvenir,
            appropriate mention on the website and announcements during
            event/workshop.<br />
            4. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>EXHIVISION ₹30,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. 'Exhivision' is a platform where innovative and application-based
            projects are showcased.<br />
            2. This event always have a huge hit among the participants where
            they are excited to brainstorm with new and creative ideas. <br />3.
            Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>REFRESHMENT SPONSOR ₹50,000</h2>
          <p>
            1. Logos on posters, banners, and a half page advertisement in the
            souvenir and appropriate mention on the website.<br />
            2. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <h2>MEDIA SPONSOR</h2>
          <p>
            1. Logos on posters, banners and a half page advertisement in the
            souvenir and appropriate mention in the website.<br />
            2. Promotions will be done on the Instagram and Facebook handles.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="form-container">
      <form>
        <div class="title"><p>Sponsorship details</p></div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="field">
            <input
              type="text"
              placeholder="Sponsor/company name"
              autocomplete="nope"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="Email"
              autocomplete="nope"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <textarea placeholder="message..." cols="20" rows="5"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button class="field btn" type="submit">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <section class="footer"><%- include('../partials/footer'); %></section>
  </body>
</html>
